## File Naming Standards

Based on Arno's Next.js architecture guide, follow these naming conventions for consistency and clarity.

## Service & Manager Files

### Service Files
- **Pattern**: `*.service.ts`
- **Location**: [src/services/](mdc:src/services)
- **Examples**:
  - [blog.service.ts](mdc:src/services/blog.service.ts)
  - [admin.service.ts](mdc:src/services/admin.service.ts)
  - [generation.service.ts](mdc:src/services/generation.service.ts)

### Manager Files
- **Pattern**: `*.manager.ts`
- **Location**: [src/managers/](mdc:src/managers)
- **Examples**:
  - [blog.manager.ts](mdc:src/managers/blog.manager.ts)
  - [validation.manager.ts](mdc:src/managers/validation.manager.ts)
  - [ai.manager.ts](mdc:src/managers/ai.manager.ts)

## Component Files

### React Components
- **Pattern**: `*.tsx` for components, `*.ts` for utilities
- **Structure**: Each component in its own directory with `index.tsx`
- **Examples**:
  - [src/components/Header/index.tsx](mdc:src/components/Header/index.tsx)
  - [src/components/Estimator/index.tsx](mdc:src/components/Estimator/index.tsx)

### Client vs Server Components
- **Client Components**: `*.client.tsx` (client-side only)
- **Server Components**: `*.server.tsx` (server-side only)
- **Shared Components**: `*.shared.tsx` (universal)

## Type Definitions

### TypeScript Types
- **Pattern**: `*.ts` for type files
- **Location**: [src/types/](mdc:src/types)
- **Examples**:
  - [src/types/index.ts](mdc:src/types/index.ts) - Common interfaces
  - [src/types/estimator.ts](mdc:src/types/estimator.ts) - Domain-specific types

### Interface Naming
```typescript
// Service interfaces
interface BlogServiceResult<T> extends ServiceResult<T> {}

// Manager interfaces
interface BlogManagerOptions {
  locale?: string;
  status?: 'published' | 'draft';
}

// Component props
interface HeaderProps {
  locale: string;
  isOpen?: boolean;
}
```

## Constants & Configuration

### Constants Files
- **Pattern**: `*.ts` for constants
- **Location**: [src/constants/](mdc:src/constants)
- **Examples**:
  - [src/constants/index.ts](mdc:src/constants/index.ts) - General constants
  - [src/constants/estimator.ts](mdc:src/constants/estimator.ts) - Domain constants

### Constant Naming
```typescript
// Use SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE for constants
export const API_ENDPOINTS = {
  BLOG_POSTS: '/api/blog/posts',
  ADMIN_POSTS: '/api/admin/posts'
} as const;

export const UI_CONFIG = {
  SCROLL_THRESHOLD: 100,
  ANIMATION_DURATION: 300
} as const;
```

